query:
ALTER TABLE siteEvaluations 
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS visibility ENUM('excellent', 'good', 'fair', 'poor'),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS isBlocked INT DEFAULT 0,
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS blockingDesc TEXT,
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS floorLevel VARCHAR(32),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS isMainDiningFloor INT DEFAULT 0,
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS nearEscalator INT DEFAULT 0,
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS isMiddleOfFloor INT DEFAULT 0,
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS nearPopularBrand INT DEFAULT 0,
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS nearPopularBrandName VARCHAR(128),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS hasShapeDefect INT DEFAULT 0,
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS shapeDefectDesc TEXT,
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS hasEngineeringDefect INT DEFAULT 0,
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS engineeringDefectDesc TEXT;
